267
00:32:27,458 --> 00:32:28,625
Butr!

268
00:32:31,041 --> 00:32:32,166
What are you doing?

269
00:32:32,833 --> 00:32:34,083
Let's go boating.

270
00:32:50,125 --> 00:32:52,416
