277
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:02,041
It was just an accident, Tiw.

278
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:05,458
No one ever wanted it to happen.

279
00:34:11,458 --> 00:34:14,125
I just wish it was just a dream

280
00:34:17,458 --> 00:34:19,708
and I would wake up soon.

281
00:34:20,875 --> 00:34:22,833
It's been more than a year, Nan.

282
00:34:45,875 --> 00:34:47,083
Hello.

283
00:34:52,375 --> 00:34:54,666
Nan, someone's calling you.

284
00:34:58,375 --> 00:34:59,416
