I'm sorry.

287
00:35:32,083 --> 00:35:33,625
You don't need to say sorry to me.

288
00:35:34,375 --> 00:35:36,750
You didn't leave me at the orphanage.

289
00:35:39,625 --> 00:35:41,625
I was in the final year at university.

290
00:35:41,708 --> 00:35:43,500
And because I got pregnant,
I had to drop out.

291
00:35:46,291 --> 00:35:49,625
That man didn't even care.
He didn't take any responsibility.

292
00:35:51,458 --> 00:35:54,500
I didn't even dare to tell my parents.

293
00:35:57,166 --> 00:36:00,208
I was so scared and not ready then.

294
00:36:11,541 --> 00:36:14,958
And how is he now?

295
00:36:19,375 --> 00:36:21,000
Now he has good fathers,

296
00:36:24,500 --> 00:36:26,625
but every kid needs a mother.

297
00:36:32,416 --> 00:36:34,458
I'm sorry. It could be my karma.

298
00:36:38,291 --> 00:36:40,125
I had a new baby boy,

299
00:36:47,125 --> 00:36:48,416
but he's gone.

300
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,500
Would you like to see him?

301
00:37:06,375 --> 00:37:07,708
Rattiya is really meddlesome.

302
00:37:09,458 --> 00:37:10,541
So much.

303
00:37:10,750 --> 00:37:12,041
Just ignore her.

304
00:37:13,041 --> 00:37:14,791
He is your son by law anyway.

305
00:37:16,333 --> 00:37:20,000
But that woman might be his birth mother.

306
00:37:21,791 --> 00:37:23,291
But we've raised him.

307
00:37:24,333 --> 00:37:25,625
