308
00:37:25,708 --> 00:37:28,083
we will win by all means
because she abandoned him.

309
00:37:31,125 --> 00:37:32,666
By law, yes.

310
00:37:34,291 --> 00:37:36,166
But law cannot be applied to everything,

311
00:37:37,291 --> 00:37:39,166
especially when it comes to feelings.

312
00:37:43,125 --> 00:37:44,791
Then don't let her see our son.

313
00:37:46,708 --> 00:37:47,750
That might be the way.

314
00:37:48,583 --> 00:37:52,583
Anyway, we should go tomorrow
and see what they have to say.

315
00:38:14,541 --> 00:38:15,666
I'm sorry.

316
00:38:18,833 --> 00:38:20,708
I know I was a bad mother.

317
00:38:24,708 --> 00:38:28,125
Actually, just knowing that he is happy,
I'm already glad.

318
00:38:30,458 --> 00:38:33,375
But now that I know he wants
to have a mother, I feel so guilty.

319
00:38:41,916 --> 00:38:44,125
Knowing he wants to see me,

320
00:38:47,375 --> 00:38:49,250
I feel even worse.

321
00:38:50,833 --> 00:38:55,833
I just want to see him and make up
for what I did.

322
00:38:55,916 --> 00:39:00,166
Without a mother, Butr is already pitiful.

323
00:39:00,958 --> 00:39:04,125
Do you want him to know
that his own mother abandoned him?

324
00:39:06,625 --> 00:39:07,875
You left him,

325
00:39:10,458 --> 00:39:12,000
and now you wanna see him
when you want.

326
00:39:13,541 --> 00:39:14,833
Don't you think
you're a little too selfish?

327
00:39:19,125 --> 00:39:24,166
I must apologize
for my wife's selfishness.

328
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:31,500
But I believe your beloved son
somehow wants to see his own mother.

329
00:39:39,166 --> 00:39:40,041
Mr. Phoon, Mr. Yuke,

330
00:39:42,666 --> 00:39:46,791
though Butr is Mr. Phoon's
adopted son by law,

331
