we are his fathers.

423
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:54,958
But he doesn't understand
our relationship.

424
00:50:57,333 --> 00:50:58,458
What do you mean?

425
00:51:00,041 --> 00:51:01,166
Like…

426
00:51:05,041 --> 00:51:07,333
if we behave like friends or brothers,

427
00:51:09,000 --> 00:51:11,000
it might be easier
for him to understand us.

428
00:51:16,916 --> 00:51:18,333
What about the registration?

429
00:51:18,666 --> 00:51:19,958
I'm also worried about this.

430
00:51:21,458 --> 00:51:25,250
If we register our marriage,
society will know.

431
00:51:26,500 --> 00:51:29,125
Butr's official documents will
be visible for the rest of his life.

432
00:51:30,750 --> 00:51:33,583
I think we'd better postpone it.

433
00:51:34,500 --> 00:51:37,000
It's not too late to do it
after we consider it carefully.

434
00:51:39,875 --> 00:51:41,000
Also,

435
00:51:41,708 --> 00:51:46,208
same-sex love is not all about
marriage registration.

436
00:51:47,791 --> 00:51:50,375
It's more important
to understand each other.

437
00:51:51,875 --> 00:51:54,916
There are a lot of normal couples
who don't register their marriage.

438
00:51:58,208 --> 00:51:59,583
Like Tul and his girlfriend?

439
00:52:03,125 --> 00:52:05,458
The girl's family took the kid away

440
00:52:05,833 --> 00:52:08,333
and doesn't even allow Tul
to register himself as father.

441
00:52:10,000 --> 00:52:15,708
Now Tul has no right to his son
and wastes time suing his girlfriend,

442
00:52:18,250 --> 00:52:21,583
even though they're a normal couple.

443
00:52:31,125 --> 00:52:35,333
Right now only you have the right to Butr.

444
00:52:37,458 --> 00:52:39,250
If something unexpected happened,

445
00:52:40,541 --> 00:52:42,375
I would become someone
without a legal relationship to Butr.

446
00:52:42,458 --> 00:52:43,750
I understand,

447
00:52:44,708 --> 00:52:46,291
but… Yuke!

448
00:52:47,791 --> 00:52:48,875
Yuke!

449
00:53:20,416 --> 00:53:21,791
What are you doing?

450
00:53:24,458 --> 00:53:26,250
Don't you have your own?

451
00:53:27,166 --> 00:53:28,833
